				<div class="et_pb_slide_content"><div id="attachment_1746" style="width: 699px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><a href="https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2015/05/RJD_04_01_0014_0008_001.jpg" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img class="wp-image-1746" src="https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2015/05/RJD_04_01_0014_0008_001-1024x804.jpg" alt="Richard J. Daley with cake celebrating the 120th anniversary of the incorporation of the City of Chicago, ca. 1957. Photo: Pics Chicago. RJD_04_01_0014_0008_001" width="689" height="541" srcset="https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2015/05/RJD_04_01_0014_0008_001-1024x804.jpg 1024w, https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2015/05/RJD_04_01_0014_0008_001-300x236.jpg 300w, https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2015/05/RJD_04_01_0014_0008_001-1080x848.jpg 1080w, https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2015/05/RJD_04_01_0014_0008_001.jpg 1500w" sizes="(max-width: 689px) 100vw, 689px" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">Richard J. Daley with cake celebrating the 120th anniversary of the incorporation of the City of Chicago, ca. 1957. Photo: Pics Chicago. RJD_04_01_0014_0008_001</p></div>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<div id="attachment_1095" style="width: 1034px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><a href="https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2015/05/RJD_04_01_0052_0006_013.jpg" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img class="wp-image-1095 size-large" src="https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2015/05/RJD_04_01_0052_0006_013-1024x684.jpg" alt="Apollo 11 astronaut parade crowd to celebrate first man landing on the moon" width="1024" height="684" srcset="https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2015/05/RJD_04_01_0052_0006_013-1024x684.jpg 1024w, https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2015/05/RJD_04_01_0052_0006_013-300x200.jpg 300w, https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2015/05/RJD_04_01_0052_0006_013-1080x721.jpg 1080w, https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2015/05/RJD_04_01_0052_0006_013.jpg 1500w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">Apollo 11 astronaut parade crowd to celebrate landing of first man on the moon, 1969. RJD_04_01_0052_0006_013</p></div></div>
							
