							<h2 class="et_pb_slide_title">7 of 18</h2>
				<div class="et_pb_slide_content"><div id="attachment_1079" style="width: 1034px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><a href="https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2015/05/RJD_04_01_0036_0006_003.jpg" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img class="wp-image-1079 size-large" src="https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2015/05/RJD_04_01_0036_0006_003-1024x804.jpg" alt="Richard J. Daley and Eleanor Daley with costumed Mrs. O'Leary and cow, 1976. RJD_04_01_0036_0006_003" width="1024" height="804" srcset="https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2015/05/RJD_04_01_0036_0006_003-1024x804.jpg 1024w, https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2015/05/RJD_04_01_0036_0006_003-300x236.jpg 300w, https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2015/05/RJD_04_01_0036_0006_003-1080x848.jpg 1080w, https://rjd.library.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2015/05/RJD_04_01_0036_0006_003.jpg 1500w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">Richard J. Daley and Eleanor Daley with costumed Mrs. O&#8217;Leary and cow, 1976. RJD_04_01_0036_0006_003</p></div></div>
							
